{"tid":2423561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想做靚仔......","createTime":"2021-02-26T03:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:45:45.000Z","uid":258144,"like":52,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9b224f0bcff681e65d8941df50c8b4faa9e1e96b","tid":2423561,"uid":258144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"香港呢個地方 靚女&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;靚仔<br />\n平時行喺銅鑼灣旺角街頭 一個月都未必見到一次靚仔 所以話香港靚仔真係國家級稀有生物嚟<br />\n香港做靚仔一定所有女同仔都俾佢溝曬  出街食飯仲可能唔使錢<br />\n落bar靜靜地坐喺度都大把女同仔approach <br />\n出街肯定比所有人望到實一實<br />\n仲會周不時比連登仔放上嚟意淫<br />\n冇錢又可以去跳下老舞幫補家計<br />\n有抑鬱又可以打造悲劇主角嘅光環<br />\n而且同人做愛又唔使好似靚女咁擔心俾人中岀即飛 諗落都覺得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18ea697ab7073d98fb7899b560f7d83f8caf6d7","tid":2423561,"uid":188322,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"張偉健夠唔夠靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未又係俾女友厭窮冇將來,俾人飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁既情況仲撚hurt<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1ff24e88b0dd5da1fd4bf568228556294b0fbf","tid":2423561,"uid":361584,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"疫情冇左，口罩冇左，先開post 啦"},{"pid":"650f4c78b45d1bb0bd735986075c682be86d8de3","tid":2423561,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fro